title: Dragonforce - Ultra Beatdown [2008]
description:
Ultra Beatdown is the upcoming fourth studio album by power metal band DragonForce, to be released on 20 August 2008 in Japan through JVC and on 25 August 2008 worldwide through Roadrunner Records and Universal Music.
